# AgenticApps workflow — canonical project ignores.
#
# POLICY (ADR-0037): phase artifacts under `.planning/phases/` are COMMITTED.
# They are the shared, cross-host project plan (CONTEXT.md, PLAN.md,
# VERIFICATION.md, REVIEW.md, HANDOFF-LOG.md, …). Do NOT add a
# `.planning/phases/` (whole-tree) ignore here — it drops the planning evidence
# other hosts and future sessions rely on. See
# docs/standards/gsd-binding-and-planning.md and ADR-0037.
#
# Only local / ephemeral state is ignored below. This file is a starting
# baseline the scaffolder appends to any existing project `.gitignore`; add your
# own stack ignores (node_modules/, dist/, target/, __pycache__/, …) as needed.

# Local / ephemeral working state
.claude/worktrees/
.planning/current-phase
.planning/skill-observations/
*.tmp

# Raw reviewer scratch (consolidated into <NN>-REVIEWS.md, which IS committed)
.planning/phases/*/.codex-review.md
.planning/phases/*/.gemini-review.md
.planning/phases/*/.claude-review.md
.planning/phases/*/.review-prompt.md
